01:24:44,145 --> 01:24:46,845
- Nic, I think we should just...
- Hold on.

736
01:25:00,895 --> 01:25:03,195
Nic, stop!

737
01:25:31,059 --> 01:25:33,292
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

738
01:25:47,708 --> 01:25:50,076
I love you.

739
01:26:30,585 --> 01:26:33,351
Haley!

740
01:27:40,621 --> 01:27:43,155
Don't even think about it, Nic.

741
01:27:43,690 --> 01:27:45,891
You can't reach her.

742
01:27:53,967 --> 01:27:56,034
<i>On my side.</i>

743
01:27:59,506 --> 01:28:02,375
Take a look at yourself, Nic.

744
01:28:03,344 --> 01:28:08,311
The perfect integration
of human will and...

745
01:28:09,250 --> 01:28:11,818
alien technology.

746
01:28:13,387 --> 01:28:15,988
Our finest achievement.

747
01:28:21,929 --> 01:28:23,930
Nomad?

748
01:28:26,434 --> 01:28:28,168
Nomad!

749
01:28:28,170 --> 01:28:32,673
Nomad, yes. I brought you here.

750
01:28:32,675 --> 01:28:37,244
But remember, Nic, you were the
one who came looking for me.

751
01:28:37,246 --> 01:28:40,014
